Over the past 10 days, Bapsfontein was a hot topic of discussion among members of the Lowveld&#8217;s equestrian community. A greyish-black pony called Pixie is central to a scandal. Two women claim that Pixie is theirs.One is Ms Colleen van Rooyen. The other is Ms Shannon Jaume. Van Rooyen has opened a stock-theft case with the police and her affidavit identifies Jaume as the alleged pony thief.